short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search your history using semantic search

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have you ever forgotten what you searched recently or in the past and couldn't remember it? You definitely don't remember it enough to find it in your actual search history. You only remember vaguely what it was about, but nothing more.

Semantic Search History allows you to use the latest in NLP to look back into your past search history and turn generic thoughts into relevant search results that you've made in the past. No need to remember exact keywords, we handle that for you.
